Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Taru-chan. \NMama is also happy to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me happy too, Honmaru's mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru returned as well, so I guess we've a full party now. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, I brought this to celebrate the reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Matsu-san's takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back and eat to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Honmaru's papa. Me delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say your thanks while eating, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru's papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Both now have takoyaki all over their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If she saw this, Mimora-chan, who hates takoyaki so much, \Nwould probably make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Mimora-chan \Nmoved to Ijigawa's house to freeload there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those two are getting along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please keep it low, will you? \NIt'd be dangerous if someone notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'm letting you freeload at our house, \Nbut in secret from my family, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll make a big deal of it if they find out \Nwe're living with a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We come from a totally normal, serious family, \Nunlike that of Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, to say I won't even get my own room!? \NThat was the final straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a freeloader, remember? \NSo stop being so extravagant, you silly girl. {not really sure what exactly she means with fuzaketa and what better to make of it with next lines in mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, too bad you're the one being silly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pork-Bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Isn't that a silly face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you like your new look? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's damn noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so noisy, Rui! \NDo you have a guest over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui became a pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true! I'm not lying! \NJust go there and look at it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic will wear off in 30 minutes. Please be patient until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! I'll let you use this room however you please! \NSo please return my face back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just said so in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright! I'll go there to recheck just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. Let me use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called Pointurner. Anything you point it at \Ncan be turned into whatever you command it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For a demonstration, \Nhow about turning that cushion into a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? How many times do I have to tell you \Nto knock before entering?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui, your pig face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this nonsense you're talking about? \NHow can you call your sister's elegant face a pig's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should use some face serum? {/don't you have a bad skin; rough skin; unhealthy skin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked her more when she was a pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have preferred to be a pig's little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! I thought it'd be good to keep a magician in the house, \Nbut I made a huge mistake in my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Isn't that because you didn't speak your wish earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up, you! My wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly. I'll tell you my wish now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make me a magician myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a wish...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Don't tell me, you can't grant it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be pretty embarrassing, wouldn't it?{actually "that's not how it's supposed to be"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Is there something you can't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you one bi-i-i-i-ig
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,liar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it loud and clear before - \Nyou can make any one thing come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bare minimum for being a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't even do that, stop being so bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet, you shouldn't have said it in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being an inexperienced mess, you think you can go ahead and promise me you'd do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Mimora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's settled down already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Just as you said, \NI'm an inexperienced mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a short time, \Nbut thank you for your care. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather ask Honmaru-sama to accept me \Nthan live in such a woman's custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I'll be living with Taru-sama this way! {osewa ni?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use trying to trick your way into Honmaru's house. {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's family isn't rich enough \Nto afford two freeloaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if he finds out you're just an excuse of a magician, \Nwho can't grant even a single wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,something tells me, \NTaruruuto wouldn't be too happy with that. {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He might actually run out of patience for you. {to be disgusted with; to run out of patience; to fall out of love}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! To think that Taru-sama \Nmight ever come to dislike me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've thought it through, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I'll let you run off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to ever run away from our home, \NI'd wager no amount of excuses would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't need to worry for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, it's very easy to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I come up with another wholesome{no clue what to make of yasashi} wish, \Nall you have to do is stay quiet and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that'd be the best thing to do \Nso as to bring you and Taru closer?{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of me, Rui-chan-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that you understand! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see Iyona-chan again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mimora-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, Honmaru-sama, and Niruru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ever so polite, our Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wouldn't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Honmaru, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Ijigawa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just say hello properly, \Neven though you're clearly old enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow the little one's example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go around teaching everyone how to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody likes bastards who are too stiff.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doncha feel like you've been getting \Nstuck up lately, Honmaru? {to get conceited; to become vain; to get stuck up; to get a swollen head; to become a tengu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doncha start acting all so important \Njust 'cause you died once, you dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Only death can cure an idiot," that's what they say, \Nbut you managed to remain an idiot even after death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, Rui-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your face today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please never mind that. \NGood morning, Iyona-chan. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Iyona-chan sure is elegant and beautiful, \Nso unlike any other woman around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, you're looking even more dazzling today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Honmaru-kun, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, will you let me accompany you to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go together too, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear this, I've seen it with my own eyes! \NHis whole body is completely white! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fun, I'd say!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Not one bit fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one cute thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand humans' feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha trying here, giving me that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I feel like I've seen you somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Niruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru - my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you squeeze its tail, \Nit turns into whatever it's looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Who might this lovely girl be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a neat style \Nand a cute slanting on the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! This is actually Niruru disguised as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use Niruru to play pranks on Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much so, Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go play outside, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Honma—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Taru might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Honmaru acquired - \Nfirst part is done! {一丁上がり}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to commence the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun... Honmaru-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He took away my bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Honmaru-kun \Ndo something like that... {sounds like the opposite: is supposed to do}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I wasn't kidding. Moreover, I've just bought it. \NAnd it's brand new too! {unsure why she added that as doing this to used/old ijigawa's underwear would've been obviously more vindicating towards honmaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return it to Rui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are his true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you be doing something like this? \NHonmaru-kun, answer me seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru amazing! Complete perv. \NA complete perv, just like the original!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, so that's where you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! The real one is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Use your magic to turn Honmaru \Ninto a chair or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse! I'm not your servant or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being bossed around! {命令するのは許してくだされ!  - no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I wonder whose house you're freeloading at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To your ultimate benefactor, who even agreed to take this inexperienced magician under her wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you think it's an acceptable thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can throw your sorry ass out anytime!{g, maybe "you can leave anytime"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, why are you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cha-a-a-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... Just now, I saw Honmaru-kun behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NYou just imagined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stop, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora used Pointurner \Nto make Honmaru a chair! Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I got turned into a chair by Mimora-chan's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, it's not me! \NWhat kind of weird things is he doing to Iyona? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That "Honmaru" is actually Niruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your act together, Honmaru-k—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Well, isn't our Honmaru a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This was another one of Ijigawa's tricks! \NMan, this is serious! Help me, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Funny! Playing pull or push!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Easy for you to stay cheerful \Nwhen you don't know how others feel!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How may I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's some magic \Nto control Niruru as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This selfish woman keeps making too many requests!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go to the streets anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Limpimpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you can control freely \Nthe movements of anyone you're pointing your finger at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Lend it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What is she going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This sounds fun already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that weird posture? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stop it, Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Niruru funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is getting really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Rattle-rattle-rattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your rattle-rattle right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Honmaru! You sick scum! {/doing hentai things}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the devil of a woman, Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru-kun, tell me what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to return to your usual self!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Honmaru-kun would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was your fault to begin with, Honmaru! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. Should I leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But using this thing can be quite addictive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then... He used this magic on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You were the one who played around with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll pay you back in your own coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rui, what's that? Limpimpy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's go for "squeeze-squeeze," is that how it goes? {/had been}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna play too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, I said! {/let go}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My! How dare you do such things to my Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Honmaru-sama! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? You're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pull you up slowly! Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all that to save me! It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, my hair is all frizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ijigawa? \NDoes it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course I'm not okay, you freak! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't I even get a "thank you" for saving you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You did that just so that you could \Npeek into under my skirt all you want! {/despite peeking all the way ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd Honmaru do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all alone up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Rui-chan, you saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What Honmaru-kun did to my clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really dress up like that to school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, weren't you just seeing \Na bad dream or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I probably did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun would never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course he wouldn't, silly girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm the weird one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It was a dream! A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what really happened! {/let's see once more}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Stop time with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimama! Time, stop! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now make a beeline for Iyona-chan's house \Nand get her some new clothes!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then change her clothes quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Unfreeze the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! That woman is a natural-born taskmaster! {working one's employees hard; being a slave-driver}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one weird dream you saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She made it right with Mimora's magic. {/cheated well}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui really a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that? \NBut I'm glad all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this very weird dream I saw, \NI made wrong conclusions about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, alright! Don't worry one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I can forgive anything to Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ijigawa. You're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who really saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that I'll never turn my back on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, wanna come home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I went home with Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Honmaru and Niruru not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hurry home! {no clue, tlc?}{22:09: I'm hearing "早くおきましょう"\NNot sure about this one. "起きる" doesn't make much sense to me in this context.\NI think a simple "Let's hurry" should be fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If that woman comes, \Nthere goes our peaceful life! {lib}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder where Honmaru-kun could have gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand! \NSuch strength in a girl...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl's heart works in mysterious ways...{/is a complicated thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fun, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, barefoot! Barefoot seems fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my boots off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Taru! Playing beach volleyball in the middle of winter is what the doctor ordered! {no clue whatsoever}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Teacher and Rival are mysteriously excited today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This might as well be happening in a spokon manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, children belong to the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival's Unrequited Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mimora is rooting for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:05.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 65 \NRival's Unrequited Love {ライバーの片想い}
